00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:44.360
Señor,

00:08:44.560 --> 00:08:45.360
Ya lo he comprobado.

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:46.940
Ella es doctora.

00:08:47.240 --> 00:08:50.040
Escuché que ella curó las migrañas de Chen Jingbian.

00:08:50.240 --> 00:08:51.700
